  <summary date="2019-01-17T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Restricting First Use of Nuclear Weapons Act of 2019

This bill prohibits the President from conducting a nuclear strike against an enemy that did not first launch a nuclear strike against the United States or a U.S. ally, unless Congress expressly authorizes such a strike.</summary>
